Xt rng:
Bn A l mt cng ty c thnh lp v hot ng hp php theo php lut Vit Nam, c y nng lc v iu
kin cung cp dch v t chc cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch.
Bn B l mt Cng ty c thnh lp v hot ng hp php theo php lut Vit Nam, c y nng lc hot
ng trong lnh vc thng mi in t v mua bn sn phm tour/dch v du lch.
Do vy, cc bn tha thun v ng k kt hp ng vi nhng iu khon nh sau:
IU 1: GI BN SN PHM TOUR/DCH V DU LCH V PHNG THC THANH TON
1.1 Bn A cung cp gi i l ca cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch cho bn B. Bn B c quyn bn cho Khch
hng vi gi cao hn gi i l.
1.2 Cn c vo Yu cu t v cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch trc tuyn trn website divui.com t khch hng,
bn B trc tip thu tin cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch. Bn B gi Yu cu t v cc sn phm tour/dch v
du lch cho bn A v thanh ton cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch ny cho bn A vi mc gi dnh cho i l.
IU 2: GI I L
Gi i l: L mc gi ca cc Sn phm Tour/Dch v du lch m bn A nim yt dnh cho cc i tc i l phn phi.
Mc gi i l ca cc sn phm Tour/Dch v du lch m bn A nim yt phi lun thp hn mc gi m bn A nim yt
dnh cho khch hng trc tip ca bn A.
- Gi i l k s c bo m v c gi tr trong 01 (mt) nm k t ngy k. Trong trng hp 1 trong 2
bn c yu cu thay i v gi hoc cc iu khon trong hp ng, s p dng vn bn thay i theo quy nh
php l.
IU 3: QUYN V TRCH NHIM CA CC BN
3.1 Trch nhim v quyn hn ca bn A
a. Bn A cung cp chi tit ni dung cc Sn phm Tour/Dch v du lch theo tha thun
b. Cung cp thng tin cho bn B v cc Sn phm Tour/Dch v du lch mi v thng tin khuyn mi (nu c).
c. Khi c thay i v gi, bn A c trch nhim gi vn bn thng bo gi mi cho bn B ngay lp tc. Bn B s
xc nhn gi mi bng vn bn. Bn B s khng chu bt c trch nhim no lin quan n vic sai gi trong
trng hp Bn B khng nhn c yu cu thay i gi t Bn A.
d. Chu trch nhim trc php lut v gii trnh vi cc c quan c thm quyn v cht lng, tnh hp php ca
dch v do bn A cung cp cng nh cc khiu ni v dch v (nu c) ca Khch hng.
e. Cung cp chnh xc cc sn phm tour/dch v du lch& cc dch v i km cho Khch hng theo cc thng tin
t Yu cu t v ca bn B.
f. Bn A c trch nhim tn trng, khng c c hnh vi lm nh hng n thng hiu v uy tn ca bn B
trc khch hng.
g. Bn A s xut ha n cho Bn B theo gi thu ca i l trong vng 01 tun k t ngy nhn c ngh xut
ho n t bn B.
3.2 Trch nhim v quyn hn ca bn B
a. Gii thiu chnh xc cc Sn phm Tour/Dch v du lch ca bn A theo ni dung trong Hp ng & Ph lc.
b. T ngy 01 - 05 hng thng, bn A gi bng i sot cng n cho bn B. T 01 05 ngy (khng tnh th 7 v
ch nht) k t ngy c email hai bn xc nhn cng n chnh xc, bn B phi thanh ton y 100% cho bn A
theo gi bn i l bn A p dng cho bn B. Mi s thanh ton chm tr, bn B phi chu bi thng theo mc li
sut ngn hng Vietcombank quy nh ti thi im thanh ton.
c. Bn B s chuyn khon vo ti khon ca bn A nh sau:
1. Tn ti khon: Cng Ty C Phn Vit Nam Travelmart
S ti khon: 004.1000.178.393 ti Ngn hng ngoi thng Nng - (Vietcombank Nng)
Hoc 2. Tn ti khon:
S ti khon: 200014851232220 Ti Eximbank CN HCM
d. Bn B chu trch nhim xut ho n cho khch hng
IU 4: QUY NH V T V V XC NHN
4.1 t v
a. Khch hng ca Bn B (Khch hng) khi c nhu cu s tin hnh t v trn h thng ca Bn B. Ngay sau khi
Khch hng ca Bn B t v v thanh ton thnh cng, trn h thng ca Bn B s gi qua email cho Khch hng
V s dng dch v (Voucher) theo mu c quy nh ti Ph lc nh km theo Hp ng ny
b. Bn B s tng hp v gi Yu cu t v (Booking) cho Bn A v tng s t v m Khch hng t km vi
thng tin ca Khch hng, vic gi thng bo ny s c gi bng email
c. Bn A khi nhn Yu cu t v (Booking) do Bn B gi sang phi xc nhn kh nng cung cp dch v qua email
trong vng 24 gi. Sau khi Bn A xc nhn, Bn B tin hnh thanh ton theo chi tit trong iu 3.2 ca hp ng
ny.
d. Trng hp bn A nhn Yu cu t v (Booking) do bn B gi sang nhng bn A khng cung cp c dch v
theo ni dung bn A gi cho bn B ng ti trn h thng ca bn B th bn A phi c trch nhim thng bo li
cho bn B trong vng 24 gi v tm mt dch v tour khc cng hnh trnh, c gi tr tng ng cho khch hng
v bn A s phi chu mi chi ph pht sinh nu c.
4.2 Cung cp dch v
a. Bn A da trn Yu cu t v (Booking) do bn B gi sang c trch nhim lin h v cung cp dch v cho khch
hng theo tho thun
b. Khch hng ca bn B khi s dng dch v s xut trnh cho bn A V s dng dch v (Voucher) theo mu c
quy nh ti Ph lc nh km theo Hp ng ny v giy t tu thn nu cn thit
c. Bn A c trch nhim i chiu thng tin Khch hng trn V s dng dch v (Voucher) v giy t tu thn vi
Yu cu t v (Booking)
d. Mi trng hp khiu ni v vic khng cung cp dch v do thng tin ca Khch hng khng khp th Bn A
phi chuyn cho Bn B cng phi hp gii quyt.
e. Trng hp bn A t chc tour cho khch theo lch trnh, cht lng dch v khng theo ng tha thun m khng
c s ng ca bn B, bn A s phi hon tr li ton b chi ph cho khch hng nu khch hng khiu kin.
4.2 Hu/i/tr v
a. Bn B c trch nhim thng bo cho khch hng v p dng chnh sch hu/i/tr theo quy nh trong dch v ca
Bn A
b. Trng hp Bn A xc nhn kh nng cung cp dch v m, v bt k l do g khng nm trong iu 5 ca hp
ng ny, khng th cung cp dch v, Bn A s phi hon tr li ton b chi ph cho khch hng cng nh cc chi
ph bi hon pht sinh nu khch hng khiu kin.
IU 5: BT KH KHNG
- Bt kh khng l nhng s kin xy ra mt cch khch quan, khng th lng trc v khng th khc phc
c mc d p dng mi bin php cn thit m kh nng cho php.
- Nhng trng hp c coi l s kin bt kh khng bao gm nhng khng gii hn nh: ng t, l lt, hn
hn, chy, n, dch bnh, thm ha, thin tai, chin tranh, khng b, nh cng, ph sn hoc nhng s kin
khng th lng trc c v khng c ngha v phi bit trc dn n vic khng th tip tc thc hin hay
c th nh hng nghim trng ti hiu lc ca hp ng, hai bn s khng truy cu trch nhim hp ng.
IU 6: SA I V CHM DT HP NG
6.1 Sa i hp ng
- Trong qu trnh thc hin hp ng, mi sa i, b sung cc iu khon trong hp ng phi c hai bn
tha thun bng vn bn v c lp thnh ph lc ring, ph lc l mt b phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng.
6.2 Chm dt hp ng
Hp ng c th chm dt trong cc trng hp sau:
a. Mt bn ngh bng vn bn v vic chm dt hp ng trc thi hn nhng phi thng bo cho bn kia t
nht 30 (ba mi) ngy nhm trnh cc n t tour trc & nhng khon thu- chi cha c kt ton gia 2
bn.
b. Mt trong hai bn b ph sn, gii th theo qui nh ca php lut.
c. Bn A vi phm quy nh iu 3 ca Hp ng ny.
IU 7: IU KHON CHUNG
7.1 Hp ng c hiu lc 01 (mt) nm k t ngy k. Nu bn B tip tc lm i l cho bn A th hp ng s t
ng gia hn sau . Nu trc 15 (mi lm) ngy khi hp ng c ht hiu lc, bn A c thay i no khc
hai bn phi bn bc tha thun li gi c, cung cp dch v, thanh ton th bn A bo li cho bn B k hp
ng mi.
7.2 Hai bn cam kt thc hin nghim chnh cc iu khon ca hp ng. Nu bn no vi phm cc iu khon
ca hp ng s phi bi thng ton b cc chi ph pht sinh thc t do hnh vi vi phm gy ra v chu trch
nhim theo quy nh ca php lut.
7.3 Hai bn cam kt mi thng tin, ti liu lin quan n hai Bn s c bo mt tuyt i, khng tit l cho bt k
bn th ba. Cc thng tin ch c cung cp cho bn th ba khi c s chp thun bng vn bn ca c hai bn.
7.4 Trong qu trnh thc hin hp ng, nu xy ra tranh chp, hai Bn s cng thng lng, tha thun v bn
bc gii quyt. Nu trong 30 ngy m hai Bn khng thng lng gii quyt c th mt trong hai bn c
quyn a v vic ra Ta n nhn dn TPHCM gii quyt theo quy nh ca php lut Vit Nam.
7.5 Hp ng c lp thnh 02 ( hai) bn, mi bn gi 01 (mt) bn, c gi tr php l nh nhau.
